# scripts/demo/sanitize.map.example — copy to sanitize.map.local (gitignored), fill REAL values.
# Format: <REAL-VALUE><TAB><PLACEHOLDER>. Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Used by capture.sh for BOTH the sanitize substitution and the exact validate-local denylist.
# NEVER commit sanitize.map.local — it holds real identifiers.
#
# 111122223333	123456789012
# my-dev-user	ci-deployer
# my-gcp-project	example-prod
# my-org/my-repo	example-corp/web-app
# 198.51.100.23	203.0.113.10
# fd12:3456:789a:1::1	2001:db8::1
# 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000	aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee
# devbox.internal.example	host.example.com
